room_title: Escape room "The Dynaline Incident" by Quandary Escape Rooms in Sacramento
room_description: Your team has been asked to come to a meeting regarding the use of the New Dynaline Gas Formula. Unfortunately for you, when you arrive to meet Dr. Clark, you find that he is nowhere to be found, but instead are faced with a malfunctioning Dynaline Gas Dispenser! If it's not stopped, a horrible outbreak is sure to happen! Will you be the hero, shut down the machine, and retrieve the leaking canister? Only time will tell...
